How to build a sales version of dgn:
------------------------------------
- to see what version you are currently set to type
   'version'
- find out that versions are available:
  - 'showver hpmtle2'
- set to the appropriate version
  - 'ccversion B.02.50 hpmtle2'
- If your are setting to a B.02.50 version you must add one line to
  your config spec after you run 'ccversion B.02.50 hpmtle2':
  'edcs'
  Right after the line:
    element * CHECKEDOUT
  add this line:
    element .../uCC/src/future.h /main/3

   If you change from one version to another do the following:
  -----------------------------------------------------------
    - After changing from one version to another you must be sure to remove
      all libraries and objects left over from the previous version.  This
      means you must do the following commands in the following directories:
        dgn/src
        pvi/src
        tsi/src
        vmc/src
        vth/src
        pm/src
        u/src
        uCC/src
        trc/src
      cd into each of these directories and do the following:
        'make clean'
        'make lib'
    - cd into bin/src
        'make clean'
        'make' 
    - Go back to the dgn directory:
        'cd dgn/src'
    - remove the dgn library so it will be rebuilt.  This needs to
      happen so the compiler will create the ptrepository directory
      which is used when dgn_sales gets created.  This is the
      way HP's C++ compiler implements C++ templates.
        'rm libdgn.a'
    - set the appropriate C++ compiler options:
      - for a non-debug version of dgn_sales do the following:
        'export CXXOPTS="-z -DNDEBUG"
      - for a debug version of dgn_sales:
        'export CXXOPTS="-z -g"'
    - make sure that /proj/hp3070/bin/src is in your PATH environment variable
    - build the dgn_sales executable:
      'make dgn_sales'
    - cp the dgn_sales to wherever you need it, renaming it if necessary

  If you did not change versions, but you made a change to something
  in dgn/src/sales_tests, do the following to rebuild the dgn_sales
  executable.
  ------------------------------------------------------------------
    - cd dgn/src/sales_tests
      'make'
    - check that the appropriate C++ compiler options:
      - for a non-debug version of dgn_sales do the following:
        'export CXXOPTS="-z -DNDEBUG"
      - for a debug version of dgn_sales:
        'export CXXOPTS="-z -g"'
    - cd dgn/src
      'make dgn_sales'
    
Help for how to run lint on the files in dgn/src/sales_tests:
-------------------------------------------------------------
login to lint machine
version B.02.50 hpmtle2
cd dgn/src/sales_tests/vml
make
cd dgn/src/sales_tests
export LINTOPTS="-u -I../../../u/src -I../../../qcomp/src -I../../../ppb/src -I../../../vth/src -I../../../pm/src -I../../../dgn/src -I../../../trc/src"
make -k lint
